ia2016>{{cite journal|doi= 10.1126/science.aag0699|title= How do you save a wolf that's not really a wolf?|journal=Science|year=2016|last1=Morell|first1=Virginia |volume=353|issue=6300}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=vislobokova2003>Vislobokova, I., Sotnikova, M. & Dodonov, A., 2003 \u2013 Bio-events and diversity of the Late Miocene-Pliocene mammal faunas of Russia and adjacent areas \u2013 in: Reumer, J.W.F. & Wessels, W. (eds.) \u2013 DISTRIBUTION AND MIGRATION OF TERTIARY MAMMALS IN EURASIA. A VOLUME IN HONOUR OF HANS DE BRUIJN \u2013 DEINSEA 10: 563\u2013574 [ISSN 0923-9308] Published 1 December 2003</ref>\n\n<ref name=vonholdt2011>{{cite journal|doi=10.1101/gr.116301.110|pmid=21566151|title=A genome-wide perspective on the evolutionary history of enigmatic wolf-like canids|journal=Genome Research|volume=21|issue=8|pages=1294\u2013305|year=2011|last1=Vonholdt|first1=Bridgett M.|last2=Pollinger|first2=John P.|last3=Earl|first3=Dent A.|last4=Knowles|first4=James C.|last5=Boyko|first5=Adam R.|last6=Parker|first6=Heidi|last7=Geffen|first7=Eli|last8=Pilot|first8=Malgorzata|last9=Jedrzejewski|first9=Wlodzimierz|last10=Jedrzejewska|first10=Bogumila|last11=Sidorovich|first11=Vadim|last12=Greco|first12=Claudia|last13=Randi|first13=Ettore|last14=Musiani|first14=Marco|last15=Kays|first15=Roland|last16=Bustamante|first16=Carlos D.|last17=Ostrander|first17=Elaine A.|last18=Novembre|first18=John|last19=Wayne|first19=Robert K.|pmc=3149496}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=vonholdt2013>{{cite journal|doi=10.1007/s00335-012-9432-0|pmid=23064780|title=Identification of recent hybridization between gray wolves and domesticated dogs by SNP genotyping|journal=Mammalian Genome|volume=24|issue=1\u20132|pages=80\u20138|year=2012|last1=Vonholdt|first1=Bridgett M.|last2=Pollinger|first2=John P.|last3=Earl|first3=Dent A.|last4=Parker|first4=Heidi G.|last5=Ostrander|first5=Elaine A.|last6=Wayne|first6=Robert K.}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=vonholdt2016>{{cite journal|doi=10.1126/sciadv.1501714|pmid=29713682|pmc=5919777|