y Stadium]]||20,532||[[Swansea]]||{{WAL}}||[[Ospreys (rugby union)|Ospreys]]\n|-\n|  ||[[Headingley Stadium]]||20,500||[[Leeds]]||{{ENG}}||[[Yorkshire Carnegie]]\n|-\n|66\n|[[Perth Oval]] || 20,500 || [[Perth]] || {{AUS}} || [[Western Force]]\n|-\n| 67 ||[[Stade des Alpes]] || 20,068 || [[Grenoble]] || {{FRA}} || Most [[FC Grenoble]] matches\n|-\n| 68 ||[[Rio Tinto Stadium]] || 20,008 || [[Sandy, Utah|Sandy]] || {{USA}} || [[Utah Warriors (rugby union)|Utah Warriors]]\n|-\n| 69 ||[[Concord Oval]] || 20,000 || [[Concord, New South Wales|Concord]] || {{AUS}} || Some [[Greater Sydney Rams]] matches, [[West Harbour RFC]]\n|-\n| || [[Leichhardt Oval]] || 20,000 || [[Leichhardt, New South Wales|Leichhardt]] || {{AUS}} || [[Sydney Stars]]\n|-\n| || [[North Sydney Oval]]||20,000||[[Sydney]]||{{AUS}}||[[Northern Suburbs Rugby Club]]\n|-\n| || [[Owen Delany Park]]||20,000||[[Taupo]]||{{NZL}}||[[King Country Rugby Football Union]]\n|-\n| || [[Stade Jean-Bouin]] || 20,000 || [[Paris]] || {{FRA}} || [[Stade Fran\u00e7ais]], [[France Sevens]] (2016\u2013present)\n|-\n| 70 ||[[Baypark Stadium]]||19,800||[[Mount Maunganui]]||{{NZL}} || [[Bay of Plenty Steamers|Bay of Plenty Rugby Union]]\n|-\n| 71||[[Dick's Sporting Goods Park]]||19,680||[[Commerce City, Colorado|Commerce City]]||{{USA}}||[[Denver Barbarians]]\n|-\n| 72 ||[[Meadow Lane]]||19,588||[[Nottingham]]||{{ENG}}||[[Nottingham RFC]]\n|-\n| 73 || [[Stadio Euganeo]] || 19,500 || [[Padua]] || {{ITA}} || \n|-\n| ||[[Stade Ernest-Wallon]] ||19,500||[[Toulouse]]||{{FRA}} || [[Stade Toulousain]]\n|-\n| 74 ||[[Queenstown Events Centre]]||19,000||[[Queenstown, New Zealand|Queenstown]]||{{NZL}}|| Some [[Highlanders (rugby union)|Highlanders]] matches\n|-\n| 75 || [[Stadio Brianteo|Brianteo Stadium]] || 18,500 || [[Milan]] || {{ITA}} || Aironi Rugby\n|-\n| || [[Stade de la M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e]] || 18,555 ||[[B\u00e9ziers]]||{{FRA}} || [[AS B\u00e9ziers H\u00e9rault]]\n|-\n| 76 || [[RDS Arena]]||18,500||[[Dublin]] || {{IRL}} || [[Lei